import re


def buy_newspaper(s1, s2):
    p = re.sub(r"(.)", r"\1?", s1)
    return -1 if set(s2) - set(s1) else len(re.findall(p, s2)) - 1

def buy_newspaper(s1,s2):
    if not all(i in s1 for i in s2):return -1
    copy,i = s1,1
    while True:
        pos = [float('-inf')]
        for k in s2:
            t = next((o for o, p in enumerate(s1) if p == k and o > pos[-1]), -1)
            if t == -1 : break
            pos.append(t)
        else : return i
        s1 += copy ; i += 1

import re
def buy_newspaper(s1,s2):
    m = re.findall("".join((i+"?" for i in s1)),s2)[:-1]
    return len(m) if "" not in m else -1
